headline: Jacobs to Support the Delivery of PsiQuantum's New Quantum Computing Facility
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) was selected by PsiQuantum, a global leader in quantum computing, as the Owner's Representative for its new quantum computing facility at the Illinois Quantum and Microelectronics Park in Chicago, delivering end-to-end support across design and construction.
